reviews.title: Needs more
reviews.comment: This is great, but I find myself constantly losing at a very high level and that\'s it. There\'s no way to prolong the game. Maybe there can be a way of earning more tries or a way of skipping the jump, either by using points or even in-game money? Just throwing out ideas, but that would really improve the game!
